JuffEd
Simple text editor with syntax highlighting
Copyright (C) 2007-2008 Mikhail Murzin <mezomish@gmail.com>

Requirements:
	Qt (>= 4.2)
	QScintilla2 (>= 2.1)
	
Installation:
	*nix:
		$ ./configure
		$ make
		$ sudo make install
		(to install to fake root folder for further packaging use 'make FAKE_ROOT=<path> install')

	Windows (using MinGW):
		> mingw32-make -f WinMakefile

 License:
	JuffEd is distributed under the GNU General Public License.
	See COPYING for details.

Features:
	- multi-document interface (tabs)
	- syntax highlighting
	- code blocks folding
	- sessions support
	- find/replace using regular expressions
	- charset selection
	- line markers
	- international languages support
	
Homepage:
	https://sourceforge.net/projects/juffed/
	
Bugs and feature requests:
	https://sourceforge.net/tracker/?group_id=205470
